  "detailed_description": "In Lee inside TV you have to think outside the box and use the classical mechanics of platformer games to solve puzzles and or finish the level.<br>- Each level has a new challenge and new mechanics to use<br>- Over than 50 levels (more levels are coming!) <br>- Almost 20 collectibles and each one is also a Steam Achievement (the collectibles will show on your room after you get them). It'll be fun!<br>- Pay attention to the texts with tips in the levels and use them (sometimes literally)<br>- Nice pixel art graphics and chiptune soundtrack<br><strong></strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1170110/extras/461f028409d825d6ce3b4fbcc6d2c773.poster.avif?t=1607025007\" width=600 height=316 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1170110/extras/461f028409d825d6ce3b4fbcc6d2c773.webm?t=1607025007\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1170110/extras/461f028409d825d6ce3b4fbcc6d2c773.mp4?t=1607025007\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong></strong><br>Story:<br>Lee is just a regular straw-man boy that is broken and has a room that looks empty and has no style. <br>To solve this problems he decided to join a TV show called \"One Screen Challenge\" to make some money and get some nice hidden collectibles.<br>What he didn't know is that this TV show would somehow put him inside the TV to face dangerous challenges...<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1170110/extras/4d22a7fb06b3dd1ebfb054ae26261ede.poster.avif?t=1607025007\" width=600 height=316 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1170110/extras/4d22a7fb06b3dd1ebfb054ae26261ede.webm?t=1607025007\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1170110/extras/4d22a7fb06b3dd1ebfb054ae26261ede.mp4?t=1607025007\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
  "about_the_game": "In Lee inside TV you have to think outside the box and use the classical mechanics of platformer games to solve puzzles and or finish the level.<br>- Each level has a new challenge and new mechanics to use<br>- Over than 50 levels (more levels are coming!) <br>- Almost 20 collectibles and each one is also a Steam Achievement (the collectibles will show on your room after you get them). It'll be fun!<br>- Pay attention to the texts with tips in the levels and use them (sometimes literally)<br>- Nice pixel art graphics and chiptune soundtrack<br><strong></strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1170110/extras/461f028409d825d6ce3b4fbcc6d2c773.poster.avif?t=1607025007\" width=600 height=316 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1170110/extras/461f028409d825d6ce3b4fbcc6d2c773.webm?t=1607025007\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1170110/extras/461f028409d825d6ce3b4fbcc6d2c773.mp4?t=1607025007\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong></strong><br>Story:<br>Lee is just a regular straw-man boy that is broken and has a room that looks empty and has no style. <br>To solve this problems he decided to join a TV show called \"One Screen Challenge\" to make some money and get some nice hidden collectibles.<br>What he didn't know is that this TV show would somehow put him inside the TV to face dangerous challenges...<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1170110/extras/4d22a7fb06b3dd1ebfb054ae26261ede.poster.avif?t=1607025007\" width=600 height=316 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1170110/extras/4d22a7fb06b3dd1ebfb054ae26261ede.webm?t=1607025007\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1170110/extras/4d22a7fb06b3dd1ebfb054ae26261ede.mp4?t=1607025007\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
